        "title": "What is Digital Transformation? In the world of ecommerce, there is much discussion about undergoing digital transformation. What does it really mean?",
        "style": null,
        "contentBefore": "",
        "items": [
            {
                "text": "<p>Digital transformation refers to leveraging technology as a company to fundamentally change the way you serve your customers and deliver products. Digital transformation involves applying new technology to your existing business to create new processes that drive revenue and business growth.</p>\n"
            }
        ],
