        "id": 5,
        "type": "two-columns-text",
        "name": null,
        "title": "Selecting Technology & Partners",
        "style": null,
        "contentBefore": "",
        "items": [
            {
                "text": "<p>The next step in your transformation is to find the right technology, because the solution you choose and its architecture are going to be the core of your ecommerce business. Radical organizational change will take many turns along the way, and to accommodate the volatile nature of digital change, it is essential to rely on technology that is agile, scalable, and flexible - unlike some of the name brand monolithic solutions. Choosing an out-of-the-box solution may be convenient, but is limiting in the long run. Your implementation will touch all aspects of your enterprise &ndash; and drive your customer experience &ndash; so don&#39;t choose hastily.&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n"
            },
            {
                "text": "<p>After technology, digital transformation relies on people, and your organization working together with your partner. <strong>There is an illusion of choice when it comes to ecommerce implementation partners.</strong>&nbsp; True, certified partners, who have successfully implemented complex solutions, are few and far inbetween, and need to be&nbsp;engaged rapidly&nbsp;- because they will always have their choice of projects to pick from.&nbsp; Many so called ecommerce partners simply pay a fee for their partner label, and have limited experience.&nbsp;</p>\n"
            }
        ],
